A towering vertical maze of interconnected translucent blue and amber geometric blocks floating in a dark void, each block representing an API endpoint with glowing circuit-like pathways flowing between them. Small luminescent keys of different colors hover near specific block entrances, symbolizing role-based access gates. The structure resembles both a futuristic city skyline and a complex lock mechanism, with data streams visualized as thin ribbons of light weaving through authorized pathways while being deflected from restricted ones. Cyberpunk style with neon accents against deep purple and black backgrounds, sharp angular architecture with holographic overlays, rain droplets catching the ambient glow. The composition emphasizes the hierarchical yet interconnected nature of the system, viewed from a dramatic low angle looking upward.
